to life to figure that out.

00:39:27,122 --> 00:39:30,960
And the weird thing is you're
gonna be in a little room

00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:33,596
where people watching you 24/7.

00:39:39,902 --> 00:39:41,036
Hey.

00:39:44,006 --> 00:39:46,141
I, uh, heard they're going
to be discharging you soon.

00:39:46,141 --> 00:39:48,010
Yeah.

00:39:48,010 --> 00:39:50,880
I guess I've healed as much
as I'm going to.

00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:53,415
Well, I... I came 'cause
I wanted you to know

00:39:53,415 --> 00:39:54,783
that we arrested
the man responsible

00:39:54,783 --> 00:39:57,086
for what happened to you
and to your wife.

00:39:57,086 --> 00:39:58,754
He didn't physically
do the killings,

00:39:58,754 --> 00:40:00,623
but he is responsible.

00:40:00,623 --> 00:40:03,792
Well, I-I... I'm sorry,
I'm a little confused here.

00:40:03,792 --> 00:40:05,728
The man we arrested...

00:40:05,728 --> 00:40:07,463
lived in the motel,

00:40:07,463 --> 00:40:10,366
and he drugged
several of his guests.

00:40:11,867 --> 00:40:16,105
That night, when your wife
went to sleep,

00:40:16,105 --> 00:40:19,508
you went into the bathroom
and you snuck a cigarette.

00:40:19,508 --> 00:40:20,910
While you were in the bathroom,

00:40:20,910 --> 00:40:25,381
you were dosed with
a very potent psychedelic drug,

00:40:25,381 --> 00:40:29,518
and it caused a violent
change in your personality

00:40:29,518 --> 00:40:31,053
and your behavior.

00:40:31,053 --> 00:40:34,390
That face... that you saw...

00:40:34,390 --> 00:40:36,926
the man who was hitting
your wife...

00:40:51,907 --> 00:40:54,376
Uh... in a little while,

00:40:54,376 --> 00:40:56,912
there's going to be some
police officers coming here,

00:40:56,912 --> 00:41:00,616
and you're going to need
to go with them, okay?

00:41:00,616 --> 00:41:03,052
I'm sorry.

00:41:23,872 --> 00:41:27,443
I want to apologize
for anything I may have said

00:41:27,443 --> 00:41:28,911
while I wasn't myself.

00:41:28,911 --> 00:41:32,881
It wasn't your words so much
as your actions, really.

00:41:39,688 --> 00:41:42,658
And, obviously...

00:41:42,658 --> 00:41:44,593
I apologize for those, too.

00:41:47,563 --> 00:41:50,899
Apology accepted?

00:41:56,472 --> 00:41:57,706
Yes.

00:41:59,508 --> 00:42:00,542
(sighs with relief)

00:42:00,542 --> 00:42:01,810
Apology accepted.

00:42:01,810 --> 00:42:03,012
Good.

00:42:03,012 --> 00:42:04,380
Then you won't be trying to

00:42:04,380 --> 00:42:05,814
get back at me in some way?

00:42:05,814 --> 00:42:08,384
No, of course not.

00:42:10,019 --> 00:42:12,654
But I wouldn't drink
that coffee, if I were you.

